author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Drafty basement tips…most basements get air leaks at the rim joists. I use Great Stuff Wide Spray with the cone nozzle to fill gaps between the rim joist and wall openings. I also lightly spray the foam to speed up the cure time. This speeds up the project and makes it a fast installation.
